You can simply ask Alexa to control your Holmes Fans. Connect Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Holmes Fans" app in the app market and then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in "Holmes Fans" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with the "Alexa" app;
(4) Search for "Holmes Fans" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable "Holmes Fans" skill, and you'll be navigated to "Holmes Fans" login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Once the setup is completed. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the fan.
Alexa, turn off the fan.
Alexa, turn on the oscillation on the fan.
Alexa, turn off the oscillation on the fan.
Alexa, is oscillation on for the fan?
Alexa, set the fan speed to 1.
Alexa, set the fan speed to maximum.
Alexa, turn up the fan speed.
Alexa, decrease the fan speed by 2.
Alexa, what is the fan speed?
